WEBVTT

00:07.040 --> 00:10.800
DING

00:24.480 --> 00:27.320
You need to rest more.

00:27.400 --> 00:28.800
A head injury is no small matter.

00:28.880 --> 00:30.400
It can be serious.

00:31.080 --> 00:32.080
It's just a minor injury,

00:32.600 --> 00:33.720
nothing to worry about.

00:35.480 --> 00:36.600
But your shoulder injury,

00:36.680 --> 00:38.480
it flares up every time it rains.

00:38.560 --> 00:40.000
You've had it for five or six years now.

00:41.240 --> 00:42.120
It's nothing.

00:42.640 --> 00:44.200
The humidity in Futing makes it worse.

00:45.760 --> 00:47.720
Maybe it'll actually get better

00:48.280 --> 00:49.280
when I return to the capital.

01:05.080 --> 01:06.360
Commander Chen,

01:06.440 --> 01:09.000
what is His Majesty's purpose in summoning

01:10.280 --> 01:12.360
the Duke of Ding to the capital?

01:12.440 --> 01:15.800
How could we dare to speculate
on His Majesty's thoughts?

01:18.840 --> 01:22.160
Rest assured, General.
We deeply respect His Grace.

01:22.240 --> 01:23.960
This visit is routine business,

01:24.480 --> 01:25.800
and we'll ensure his safety.

01:26.600 --> 01:28.360
Yan Tang, enough.

01:29.160 --> 01:31.560
Stop frowning all the time. I'll be fine.

01:32.360 --> 01:34.880
His Majesty probably just wants

01:34.960 --> 01:36.320
to ask me about the maritime disaster.

01:36.400 --> 01:39.480
Take good care of your aunt when I'm away.

01:43.160 --> 01:44.480
Please, Your Grace.

02:01.440 --> 02:03.480
Grand General, the storm and tsunami
may have passed,

02:03.560 --> 02:05.640
but over a hundred families' houses
are still unrepaired.

02:05.720 --> 02:07.440
What about our relief task?

02:08.680 --> 02:11.000
Listen up, soldiers!

02:12.080 --> 02:13.600
No matter what happens,

02:14.120 --> 02:15.400
relief work must go on.

02:15.480 --> 02:17.400
As soon as the flooding is cleared,

02:18.040 --> 02:19.320
help the people get their crops planted.

02:19.400 --> 02:21.480
Only when the fields are sown

02:22.000 --> 02:23.240
will the people feel secure.

02:23.880 --> 02:24.920
Is that clear?

02:25.000 --> 02:26.160
Yes, sir!

02:32.560 --> 02:33.760
Grand General!

02:54.680 --> 02:57.480
The Duke of Ding's Residence has
been surrounded by Jiying Guards.

02:57.560 --> 02:58.400
No one is allowed in or out.

03:00.360 --> 03:01.680
What's going on?

03:05.640 --> 03:08.440
This case is far more complicated
than it seems.

03:11.880 --> 03:14.960
General, the front and back courtyards
are guarded by Jiying Guards.

03:15.040 --> 03:16.120
There must be 40 or 50 of them.

03:17.120 --> 03:19.480
If this were just a routine summons,

03:19.560 --> 03:21.480
why would there be such a show of force?

03:22.320 --> 03:25.800
General, let's storm in
and rescue His Grace's family!

03:25.880 --> 03:27.080
Yes.

03:28.160 --> 03:29.560
Don't act recklessly.

03:31.720 --> 03:32.760
Wait here for me.

03:32.840 --> 03:33.680
Yes, sir.

05:27.120 --> 05:30.560
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL BLOSSOM
BY AUTHOR ZIZI FROM QIDIAN CHINESE WEBSITE

05:35.240 --> 05:38.040
TWO WEEKS LATER

05:48.320 --> 05:49.320
Pardon our intrusion.

05:49.400 --> 05:51.880
My master's surname is Mei,
a merchant from the south.

05:52.640 --> 05:54.480
We humbly request lodging for the night.

06:09.040 --> 06:09.880
Young Lady, you're awake.

06:11.200 --> 06:12.120
What time is it?

06:13.000 --> 06:13.920
Just past the third quarter
of the Yin hour.

06:17.320 --> 06:18.360
Young Lady,

06:19.000 --> 06:20.840
a caravan arrived
at the estate seeking lodging.

06:21.440 --> 06:23.000
Their leader calls himself
Young Master Mei.

06:23.520 --> 06:25.880
But these men have calloused palms

06:25.960 --> 06:27.040
and move silently.

06:27.560 --> 06:30.680
Mr. Chen has sent people several
times asking if you're awake yet.

06:32.920 --> 06:34.400
Invite Mr. Chen over now.

06:37.080 --> 06:39.800
The servants in the estate
are very tight-lipped.

06:39.880 --> 06:42.600
All we know is that the one in charge
is referred to as Young Lady Zhao.

06:43.960 --> 06:45.000
Young Lady Zhao,

06:45.080 --> 06:48.600
I'm afraid we've encountered trouble.

06:48.680 --> 06:50.920
Those people aren't common folks.

06:51.000 --> 06:53.480
They're soldiers under the Duke of Ding.

06:53.560 --> 06:55.120
What makes you say that?

06:55.200 --> 06:58.120
The man posing as a bookkeeper,
dressed in green robes,

06:58.640 --> 07:00.920
is Yan Chao Qing.

07:01.000 --> 07:04.640
He's one of the Duke of Ding's
most trusted officers.

07:06.920 --> 07:08.600
You know him?

07:09.800 --> 07:11.440
Forgive me for deceiving you.

07:11.960 --> 07:13.480
I haven't been entirely honest

07:15.040 --> 07:17.240
-about my past.
-I know who I saw.

07:18.080 --> 07:20.640
He was once the advisor of Zhang Kai,
the former governor of Futing.

07:20.720 --> 07:23.560
His real name isn't Chen Qu Shui,

07:23.640 --> 07:24.520
it's Chen Bo.

07:24.600 --> 07:28.160
Zhang Kai? The one my uncle
executed on the battlefield?

07:30.240 --> 07:31.280
15 years ago,

07:31.360 --> 07:33.840
when the Dongyu pirates besieged Futing,

07:33.920 --> 07:36.360
Governor Zhang Kai abandoned
the city and fled for his life.

07:36.440 --> 07:39.080
He was captured and
executed by the Duke of Ding.

07:39.680 --> 07:40.840
My former master

07:41.720 --> 07:42.880
was Zhang Kai himself.

07:47.600 --> 07:48.840
Deserting the city was a grave disgrace,

07:48.920 --> 07:51.000
and Yan Chao Qing will undoubtedly see me

07:51.080 --> 07:52.400
as a dishonorable man.

07:53.120 --> 07:55.200
I've brought you trouble, Young Lady. I…

08:02.600 --> 08:03.680
Please get up, sir.

08:03.760 --> 08:06.240
GRACE UNDER THE FOREST CANOPY

08:06.320 --> 08:09.000
When I took you on as my advisor,

08:09.080 --> 08:10.640
I promised not to ask about your past.

08:11.320 --> 08:12.320
Your master's cowardice

08:13.000 --> 08:14.520
was beyond your control.

08:16.320 --> 08:17.840
What I can't figure out is…

08:18.440 --> 08:20.680
Zhending has no grain to spare

08:21.200 --> 08:22.040
and no troops to deploy,

08:22.640 --> 08:24.960
so why would they come here
under false identities?

08:25.960 --> 08:27.600
Young Master Mei is traveling with a baby.

08:28.600 --> 08:29.560
A baby?

08:33.559 --> 08:36.159
A lone minister gazes upon the cold sea

08:36.240 --> 08:39.159
Ten years of steadfast loyalty
Guarding the southeast

08:39.240 --> 08:41.840
Alas, caught in endless rainy night

08:42.360 --> 08:45.880
Where can the weeping orphan find shelter?

08:47.280 --> 08:49.040
Alas, caught in endless rainy night,

08:50.320 --> 08:52.000
where can the weeping orphan find shelter?

08:54.800 --> 08:56.280
The Duke of Ding must be in trouble.

08:58.560 --> 08:59.480
Nanny.

09:07.480 --> 09:09.280
Did he still throw up milk before sleep?

09:10.120 --> 09:11.320
It's much better since we came indoors.

09:12.040 --> 09:14.080
But after traveling for several days

09:14.160 --> 09:16.000
in the rain on bumpy roads,

09:16.080 --> 09:17.800
if we don't stop to rest,

09:18.480 --> 09:20.400
I'm worried the child won't
be able to handle it.

09:22.400 --> 09:24.840
Don't worry, we're almost there.

09:27.600 --> 09:29.680
Since ancient times, the wills
of rulers have been unpredictable.

09:30.360 --> 09:32.400
Your uncle's fate is uncertain,

09:33.240 --> 09:34.800
and with things as they are,

09:35.320 --> 09:37.360
I fear none of us
will escape this calamity.

09:38.120 --> 09:39.040
DUCHESS OF DING, MADAM LIU

09:39.120 --> 09:42.000
This is your uncle's only child.

09:42.520 --> 09:43.680
Aunt,

09:44.320 --> 09:45.240
I'll take you all with me.

09:45.320 --> 09:46.720
If you do,

09:47.480 --> 09:48.760
none of us will make it out.

09:49.520 --> 09:50.720
You know that.

09:52.360 --> 09:54.120
Promise me you'll protect him.

09:55.800 --> 09:58.120
Aunt, I swear on my life,

09:58.880 --> 10:03.040
he will not shed a single drop of blood.

10:07.400 --> 10:09.120
The Duke of Ding was deeply
favored by His Majesty.

10:09.200 --> 10:12.040
Just earlier this year, he secured
a great victory at Zhou Island

10:12.120 --> 10:14.200
and personally led the relief efforts

10:14.280 --> 10:15.600
during the typhoon and tsunami in Futing.

10:15.680 --> 10:17.760
Even our stationery shops in the capital

10:17.840 --> 10:19.160
haven't reported anything unusual.

10:19.760 --> 10:21.520
The Duke of Ding is a superior-rank duke

10:22.920 --> 10:24.320
commanding 50,000 troops in his army.

10:24.400 --> 10:26.280
If something were to happen, it
would be handled under a sealed order,

10:26.360 --> 10:27.840
with Jiying Guards
escorting him in secret.

10:28.840 --> 10:30.200
Any public disclosure
could risk a rebellion.

10:30.720 --> 10:31.960
The court can't handle that.

10:32.040 --> 10:33.720
How do you know all that, Young Lady?

10:36.640 --> 10:39.000
High merit breeds suspicion from
the throne, as it always has.

10:39.600 --> 10:40.960
As for the infant,

10:42.640 --> 10:46.040
last September we received
a letter from Futing saying

10:46.640 --> 10:48.920
His Grace's household was
purchasing baby supplies.

10:50.240 --> 10:52.840
The only one likely expecting
would be the Duchess.

10:57.240 --> 10:59.480
If this is them trying
to entrust the infant to someone

11:00.000 --> 11:01.640
before things come to pass,

11:02.840 --> 11:04.760
and they learn that I could jeopardize it,

11:04.840 --> 11:09.600
they won't leave any loose ends
that risk exposure.

11:10.720 --> 11:13.520
Do you recognize Young Master Mei?

11:16.160 --> 11:18.280
Though he's young,

11:19.040 --> 11:20.600
his presence is commanding,

11:21.120 --> 11:24.160
and the others treat him
with exceptional respect.

11:25.920 --> 11:27.240
Young,

11:28.080 --> 11:29.520
yet able to mobilize the elite forces

11:29.600 --> 11:31.880
of the Duke of Ding's Army
during such a critical time.

11:34.000 --> 11:35.320
In all the land,

11:37.200 --> 11:38.440
only Song Mo could do that.

11:38.520 --> 11:39.960
Song Mo?

11:40.040 --> 11:42.560
At thirteen, he led a surprise attack
on Yu Island.

11:42.640 --> 11:44.040
Earlier this year, during a crisis,

11:44.120 --> 11:46.200
he achieved
the great victory at Zhou Island.

11:46.720 --> 11:47.760
If it really is him,

11:48.760 --> 11:51.640
none of us will survive.

11:53.120 --> 11:54.160
We've checked.

11:54.720 --> 11:57.200
There are 42 women in the estate
and 20 servants and attendants.

11:58.080 --> 11:59.600
There's also an elderly woman

11:59.680 --> 12:01.440
being cared for by maids,
and she's already asleep.

12:02.440 --> 12:04.520
Lu Zheng and Lu Ming are guarding
the entrances securely.

12:05.120 --> 12:06.680
Everyone is in place.

12:10.320 --> 12:13.480
Young Lady, about ten people
from the caravan have disappeared.

12:14.680 --> 12:15.840
They've surrounded the estate's exits.

12:16.760 --> 12:18.000
They're going to silence everyone.

12:21.440 --> 12:22.360
Forget it.

12:22.440 --> 12:24.640
This was all caused by me.

12:24.720 --> 12:26.480
I'll take responsibility.

12:26.560 --> 12:27.640
I'll go to them.

12:27.720 --> 12:30.040
Let them kill me, and it ends there.

12:30.840 --> 12:31.840
Mr. Chen,

12:33.480 --> 12:36.200
hiding an orphan is a crime punishable
by extermination of the entire clan.

12:36.280 --> 12:37.680
If I were in their position,

12:38.200 --> 12:39.440
for the sake of the child,

12:39.520 --> 12:41.600
my soldiers, and my family,

12:41.680 --> 12:43.520
I'd do the same
and eliminate everyone here.

12:46.640 --> 12:47.600
To avoid suspicion,

12:48.120 --> 12:49.920
they'll act before sunrise,
before the rain stops.

12:51.000 --> 12:52.440
We don't have much time.

12:53.520 --> 12:55.120
Go tell Tuo Niang to lock
all the doors and windows,

12:55.800 --> 12:57.280
and don't let Grandmother be disturbed.

12:57.360 --> 12:58.200
HIDING TALENTS, WAITING TIME

13:04.960 --> 13:07.840
My Lord, they're making a move.
Should we tell our men…?

13:12.440 --> 13:14.880
My Lord, I know you've never
harmed women or children,

13:14.960 --> 13:18.600
but to protect the young lord,
there's no other way.

13:19.840 --> 13:21.880
Chen Bo is of low character,

13:22.400 --> 13:24.760
and those around him are surely no better.

13:26.160 --> 13:27.760
If word of this gets out,

13:28.880 --> 13:30.200
the consequences will be unimaginable.

13:33.440 --> 13:35.040
This is Uncle's only child.

13:35.560 --> 13:38.120
I swore before my aunt to protect him.

13:40.120 --> 13:43.240
If it means I'll face divine punishment
or go to hell,

13:44.280 --> 13:45.360
I'll bear it.

13:47.400 --> 13:48.600
Make it quick and quiet.

13:49.120 --> 13:51.240
-Don't disturb the baby.
-Yes, sir.

14:15.240 --> 14:16.480
Young Lady Zhao,

14:17.000 --> 14:18.200
where are you hurrying off to

14:18.720 --> 14:19.920
in such a storm?

14:21.120 --> 14:22.600
The wind and rain are fierce.

14:23.120 --> 14:25.480
Allow me to escort you.

14:36.120 --> 14:37.160
It's useless.

14:37.880 --> 14:38.720
They're using army crossbows.

14:39.640 --> 14:41.360
No one within a hundred paces can escape.

14:42.480 --> 14:43.480
I'm sorry.

14:51.160 --> 14:52.280
My Lord,

14:52.840 --> 14:54.560
you're making a mistake.

14:58.600 --> 14:59.520
My Lord?

15:00.200 --> 15:01.960
The Duke of Ding has been accused of
treason for defying imperial orders

15:02.040 --> 15:04.080
and using private funds
for disaster relief.

15:04.160 --> 15:06.080
He's currently being escorted to
the capital under charges of rebellion,

15:06.160 --> 15:08.080
with his entire family detained.

15:09.360 --> 15:11.640
My Lord, your bond with His Grace
is as close as father and son.

15:12.480 --> 15:13.840
Traveling in haste
on a rainy night with an infant,

15:14.720 --> 15:17.120
I suppose you're trying to hide

15:18.200 --> 15:19.760
His Grace's only bloodline.

15:21.480 --> 15:22.440
Who are you?

15:23.560 --> 15:24.880
I am an officer
of the Palace Surveillance.

15:25.480 --> 15:28.000
His Majesty anticipated your actions

15:28.640 --> 15:30.240
and ordered me to wait here

15:30.320 --> 15:31.400
to deliver his decree.

15:32.040 --> 15:33.560
Do you intend to share

15:33.640 --> 15:35.800
the Duke of Ding's charge of treason?

15:49.120 --> 15:51.800
The Palace Surveillance
is under the charge of Chen Shun.

15:53.160 --> 15:54.360
Are you one of his subordinates?

15:56.120 --> 15:57.520
Don't try to test me.

15:57.600 --> 15:59.400
There is no one named Chen Shun

15:59.960 --> 16:01.400
among the departments.

16:01.480 --> 16:02.800
Do you have an imperial token?

16:04.640 --> 16:05.720
A token…

16:43.880 --> 16:45.040
Song Mo…

16:45.640 --> 16:47.280
Since you know who I am,

16:47.920 --> 16:50.760
you must also know I've interrogated
countless corrupt officials and pirates.

16:51.280 --> 16:52.680
You grasp the nuances of court affairs

16:52.760 --> 16:54.520
well enough to mimic them convincingly.

16:55.440 --> 16:56.800
But when it comes to the details,

16:57.720 --> 16:59.400
your unease betrays you.

17:11.200 --> 17:12.040
Your palm is sweating.

17:13.760 --> 17:16.880
You couldn't have planned this alone.

17:17.920 --> 17:18.960
Who sent you?

17:20.720 --> 17:21.640
Speak,

17:22.240 --> 17:23.680
and I'll grant you a quick death.

17:26.440 --> 17:27.400
Young Lady!

17:27.480 --> 17:28.480
We got him!

17:43.560 --> 17:45.920
A diversion to buy time.

17:46.520 --> 17:47.600
You tricked me?

17:47.680 --> 17:49.200
I mean no harm.

17:49.760 --> 17:50.600
This is the only way

17:50.680 --> 17:53.760
to make you agree to sit down
and talk, My Lord.

17:53.840 --> 17:55.200
Why waste words with them, Young Lady?

17:55.280 --> 17:57.280
With the baby in our hands now,

17:57.360 --> 17:59.800
they wouldn't dare stop us
from getting you out of here.

17:59.880 --> 18:00.960
Sure!

18:01.760 --> 18:03.520
You should wake Old Madam
in the main chamber too.

18:04.280 --> 18:05.360
I'll send you all off together!

18:07.120 --> 18:08.560
SUN AND MOON ACROSS THE SKY

18:15.760 --> 18:16.840
My Lord, wait!

18:16.920 --> 18:18.120
Stop talking nonsense!

18:18.720 --> 18:21.480
We only took the baby to
ask for a chance of negotiation,

18:22.000 --> 18:23.000
not to escape.

18:23.080 --> 18:25.880
Whether it ends in bloodshed or discussion

18:26.800 --> 18:28.320
is up to you.

18:29.720 --> 18:33.440
SPRING TREES AND EVENING CLOUDS

18:33.520 --> 18:35.920
The Duke of Ding is still
en route under escort,

18:36.440 --> 18:37.960
and His Majesty's judgment
remains undecided.

18:38.040 --> 18:40.000
My Lord, you've risked
alerting the local authorities,

18:40.080 --> 18:42.280
the Ministry of Justice,
and even the Court of Judicial Review

18:42.360 --> 18:43.800
by attempting to silence everyone here.

18:43.880 --> 18:47.880
I suppose the person you intend
to entrust the child to is nearby.

18:54.280 --> 18:56.720
Tan Manor is far removed from politics

18:56.800 --> 18:57.960
and is known for
their loyalty and righteousness.

18:58.040 --> 19:00.720
I've heard the Duke of Ding once
did the Tan family a great favor

19:01.400 --> 19:02.560
They are indeed the perfect choice.

19:07.200 --> 19:09.360
This woman is cunning and full of schemes.

19:10.560 --> 19:12.880
My Lord, you must not
engage with her further.

19:13.400 --> 19:14.880
You need not see me as an enemy.

19:14.960 --> 19:18.280
I have always admired the Duke of Ding
and the Jiang family.

19:18.800 --> 19:20.320
What is his current situation?

19:21.600 --> 19:22.760
I ask

19:22.840 --> 19:24.720
because the crux of this matter

19:24.800 --> 19:25.960
isn't the child,

19:26.480 --> 19:27.720
but His Grace.

19:27.800 --> 19:29.960
If His Grace can escape his predicament,

19:30.480 --> 19:31.440
his child will naturally be safe,

19:32.720 --> 19:35.040
and you won't have to
resort to such unjust measures.

19:36.120 --> 19:38.320
His Grace's loyalty and courage
are known throughout the land.

19:38.400 --> 19:41.120
Those in court
who can discern the truth will surely

19:41.200 --> 19:42.480
submit petitions in his defense.

19:42.560 --> 19:44.640
So, it's none of your concern, Young Lady.

19:46.040 --> 19:49.320
I imagine the Duchess of Ying is
currently running from pillar to post,

19:49.840 --> 19:51.920
rallying old allies
to submit joint petitions

19:52.440 --> 19:53.360
proclaiming His Grace's innocence.

19:54.320 --> 19:56.960
Normally, that would be the right move,

19:57.560 --> 19:59.640
but the Duke of Ding is no ordinary man.

19:59.720 --> 20:01.440
Such well-intentioned efforts

20:01.960 --> 20:04.160
may very well become his death warrant.

20:06.280 --> 20:09.080
How dare a country girl like you
spout such absurd claims!

20:09.160 --> 20:10.200
You…

20:11.160 --> 20:12.520
Young Lady Zhao,

20:13.880 --> 20:15.080
please carry on.

20:16.440 --> 20:17.800
When Wang Jian demanded land,

20:17.880 --> 20:19.560
Emperor Qin simply
dismissed it with a laugh.

20:19.640 --> 20:21.200
Xiao He defamed himself,

20:21.280 --> 20:22.760
and Emperor Gaozu of Han
never doubted him.

20:22.840 --> 20:25.400
Yet Zhou Ya Fu, despite his triumph
in subduing the Seven Kingdoms,

20:25.480 --> 20:27.360
fell to slander

20:27.440 --> 20:28.960
and died in injustice.

20:29.720 --> 20:30.760
Why?

20:32.840 --> 20:34.000
When one's achievement
overshadows the ruler,

20:34.520 --> 20:36.520
it invites envy and slander from petty men

20:37.040 --> 20:38.960
seeking to deceive the Emperor.

20:40.520 --> 20:41.680
As Su Shi said,

20:42.200 --> 20:44.520
suspicion must arise first

20:44.600 --> 20:47.600
for slander to take root.

20:47.680 --> 20:50.600
If His Majesty did not already
harbor doubts,

20:51.120 --> 20:53.640
slander would never succeed.

20:53.720 --> 20:55.080
You're a traitor.

20:55.600 --> 20:56.800
What would you know
about loyalty and service?

20:57.400 --> 21:01.640
Petitions pleading innocence
challenge imperial authority.

21:01.720 --> 21:03.280
They appear as factionalism and coercion.

21:03.360 --> 21:06.000
Would such actions
ease His Majesty's doubts

21:06.080 --> 21:06.920
or deepen his mistrust?

21:11.200 --> 21:12.440
What do you think

21:13.240 --> 21:14.480
we should do then?

21:15.880 --> 21:17.000
In my opinion,

21:17.080 --> 21:18.960
why not take the opposite approach?

21:19.520 --> 21:21.240
Let the court officials turn against
the Duke of Ding and add insult to injury.

21:21.840 --> 21:24.520
If he appears isolated
and without support,

21:24.600 --> 21:27.280
His Majesty's suspicions
will naturally dissipate.

21:27.840 --> 21:29.800
Remembering their years
of service together,

21:30.640 --> 21:33.080
His Majesty will likely issue
only a minor punishment.

21:33.160 --> 21:35.040
Moving forward,
for the sake of political stability,

21:35.560 --> 21:37.840
His Majesty will surely rely
on His Grace even more.

21:39.000 --> 21:41.640
But who can truly predict
His Majesty's thoughts?

21:41.720 --> 21:44.640
Wouldn't this approach be far too risky?

21:45.280 --> 21:47.160
Young Lady Zhao, though you're
far removed from court politics,

21:48.400 --> 21:50.800
you're remarkably adept
at gauging situations

21:51.560 --> 21:53.280
and reading human nature.

22:00.240 --> 22:03.280
How do you know so much
about the Duke of Ding's case?

22:04.160 --> 22:06.200
Who are you, really?

22:06.720 --> 22:08.600
And why are you hiding out here?

22:34.040 --> 22:35.120
Nanny!

22:43.080 --> 22:45.200
Su Lan, put down your weapon.

22:45.280 --> 22:46.120
Do not act rashly.

22:47.120 --> 22:49.080
Lu Ming, let the nanny in.

23:11.400 --> 23:12.320
He's still hiccuping nonstop.

23:13.600 --> 23:15.560
Has he been like this since birth?

23:16.160 --> 23:18.000
Cold body and clammy with sweat?

23:21.160 --> 23:22.240
Su Xin,

23:22.320 --> 23:24.520
go warm up the goat's milk
I've prepared and bring it over.

23:24.600 --> 23:25.640
Yes, Young Lady.

23:26.440 --> 23:29.920
You're an unmarried young lady,
yet you know how to care for a baby?

23:30.800 --> 23:33.640
I've taken care
of many infants in the estate,

23:33.720 --> 23:35.840
so naturally, I know more than you men do.

24:13.400 --> 24:15.520
He's drinking it, he's drinking it!

24:16.080 --> 24:18.880
He's premature and frail,
unable to digest human milk properly.

24:18.960 --> 24:20.240
He needs to be fed goat's milk.

24:20.760 --> 24:23.240
Within a hundred miles,
only our estate keeps goats.

24:23.760 --> 24:25.840
I'll make sure it's delivered
to Tan Manor regularly in the future.

24:37.800 --> 24:38.640
General.

24:46.000 --> 24:46.960
Since everyone's hungry,

24:47.480 --> 24:48.600
why don't we put down our swords

24:48.680 --> 24:50.400
and share a meal together?

24:51.040 --> 24:51.880
That's a great idea!

25:05.360 --> 25:06.440
Move. Let me do it.

25:07.160 --> 25:09.200
-Fetch me a few plates.
-Got it.

25:15.920 --> 25:17.560
-Lay it here.
-Come on.

25:19.360 --> 25:20.720
Awesome!

25:20.800 --> 25:22.240
Smells so good!

25:24.760 --> 25:26.200
Dig in, guys.

25:26.280 --> 25:27.360
Here.

25:27.440 --> 25:28.520
Please help yourself.

25:29.520 --> 25:30.480
This is good!

25:30.560 --> 25:32.440
Here, have some more.

25:44.400 --> 25:46.680
Young Lady Zhao, now that
you've stepped into this mess,

25:48.000 --> 25:50.040
if Jiying Guards come investigating
and discover

25:50.720 --> 25:52.880
you knew but didn't report it,
you'll be charged with a grave crime.

25:53.840 --> 25:55.080
Do you not regret it?

25:55.720 --> 25:58.240
My Lord, you have someone
you'd risk your life to protect,

25:58.320 --> 25:59.320
and so do I.

26:00.240 --> 26:01.160
If I didn't take this risk,

26:01.680 --> 26:03.440
I wouldn't be able to save
everyone in the estate.

26:04.360 --> 26:07.440
Besides, the Duke of Ding
is someone I deeply respect.

26:10.360 --> 26:13.000
I'm poisoned. My time is running out.

26:13.840 --> 26:16.520
I only regret that I can't clear
the Duke of Ding's name before I die.

26:17.560 --> 26:19.040
Instead, I've dragged you into this.

26:21.200 --> 26:23.680
I don't want to see a man forced by fate

26:24.520 --> 26:26.120
onto a path of no return.

26:39.520 --> 26:41.080
-Move, quick!
-Move!

26:43.080 --> 26:44.120
Su Lan.

26:53.280 --> 26:54.800
Master Tan is here!

26:55.400 --> 27:00.560
BRIGHT WINDS AND CLEAR MOON

27:01.440 --> 27:03.000
Thanks to His Grace's help back then,

27:03.080 --> 27:05.080
my family has what it does today.

27:05.160 --> 27:06.040
My Lord, rest assured,

27:06.120 --> 27:08.680
I will protect His Grace's son
with my life.

27:09.280 --> 27:10.480
Master Tan, your loyalty is admirable,

27:11.040 --> 27:13.800
but today's situation calls
for extreme measures.

27:14.400 --> 27:15.560
During the recent floods,

27:15.640 --> 27:17.800
Young Lady Zhao provided relief
and sent grain,

27:17.880 --> 27:18.760
offering help and kindness.

27:19.360 --> 27:20.440
If it wasn't for her,

27:20.520 --> 27:22.480
Tan Manor wouldn't have
survived the disaster.

27:24.160 --> 27:26.880
I humbly beg for leniency.

27:27.480 --> 27:29.280
We pledge our lives
to guarantee that Young Lady Zhao,

27:29.360 --> 27:31.440
with her noble character and integrity,

27:31.520 --> 27:33.040
would never betray this secret.

27:33.560 --> 27:36.000
My Lord, please spare her and her people!

27:36.080 --> 27:38.880
My Lord, please spare her and her people!

27:45.160 --> 27:46.200
Young Lady Zhao,

27:47.320 --> 27:48.640
your estate

27:49.720 --> 27:50.680
is safe.

27:59.920 --> 28:02.040
SPRING TREES AND EVENING CLOUDS

28:02.840 --> 28:04.440
This is foxtail grass.

28:04.520 --> 28:08.320
See, doesn't it look
just like a fox's tail?

28:09.760 --> 28:12.720
Really? So this is foxtail grass.

28:15.160 --> 28:17.800
By the way, why are you here?

28:17.880 --> 28:19.320
Why aren't you going home?

28:19.840 --> 28:22.040
I don't have a home.

28:22.120 --> 28:23.440
Everyone has a home.

28:23.520 --> 28:25.360
Why don't you have one?

28:28.440 --> 28:31.320
Not everyone has a home.

28:34.920 --> 28:37.360
He feels like
a completely different person

28:37.880 --> 28:39.760
from the one I saw last night.

28:41.800 --> 28:44.360
I've long heard
of Mr. Chen's exceptional talent.

28:44.960 --> 28:48.000
How about becoming my advisor?

28:49.040 --> 28:50.960
Mr. Chen's past allegiance was misplaced.

28:51.480 --> 28:53.680
His surrender and abandonment
of the city were not his decisions.

28:54.200 --> 28:55.920
He's been with me for over ten years.

28:56.000 --> 28:57.120
He's not a dishonorable man.

28:57.200 --> 28:58.320
And if

28:59.160 --> 29:00.560
I insist?

29:02.040 --> 29:03.480
Is he trying to keep a hostage?

29:04.080 --> 29:05.360
He still doesn't trust me.

29:07.480 --> 29:08.840
Young Lady Zhao!

29:20.160 --> 29:21.520
My Lord, if you still have doubts,

29:21.600 --> 29:25.240
why not leave General Yan in the estate?

29:25.320 --> 29:27.160
Once things settle,
we can arrange an exchange.

29:27.680 --> 29:29.160
Wouldn't that be more advantageous?

29:29.240 --> 29:30.560
General Yan is one of my closest aides.

29:30.640 --> 29:32.280
How could he remain behind?

29:33.000 --> 29:35.600
And if I also insist?

29:37.960 --> 29:40.040
They've prepared some snacks
for you in the kitchen.

29:40.120 --> 29:41.400
-Go on.
-Alright!

30:06.280 --> 30:07.520
Nanny.

30:08.040 --> 30:09.120
My Lord,

30:09.640 --> 30:11.720
the young lord has fallen asleep
after having goat's milk.

30:11.800 --> 30:12.640
Good.

30:13.800 --> 30:16.040
We'll reach Tan Manor
once we cross this river.

30:16.120 --> 30:18.320
He will soon be safe and settled.

30:27.080 --> 30:29.680
-What have you found?
-We've gathered some information.

30:29.760 --> 30:31.200
She is the eldest daughter of
the Dou family from the capital

30:31.280 --> 30:32.120
Her name is Dou Zhao.

30:32.720 --> 30:34.800
Her grandmother is from
the renowned Cui clan.

30:34.880 --> 30:37.760
They say she's ruthless since her youth,
scheming to seize family assets.

30:37.840 --> 30:39.320
So, her family abandoned her
to this estate.

30:41.400 --> 30:42.440
Abandoned?

30:43.560 --> 30:45.560
Haven't I also been cast out by my father?

30:45.640 --> 30:48.840
Tales of infighting among women
in the household are never flattering.

30:50.080 --> 30:52.680
Young Lady Zhao is clever, perceptive,

30:52.760 --> 30:53.760
and highly adaptable.

30:54.280 --> 30:56.680
Her actions don't resemble
those of a typical sheltered lady.

30:56.760 --> 31:00.840
Also, the workers on her estate
are all trained fighters,

31:00.920 --> 31:03.160
and even her personal maids
are skilled in martial arts.

31:04.160 --> 31:06.560
Her father works in
the Ministry of Revenue,

31:06.640 --> 31:07.960
and her uncle, Dou Shi Shu,
was recently promoted

31:08.040 --> 31:08.960
to a senior post in the Ministry of Rites.

31:09.040 --> 31:12.280
Last night's events are likely
more complex than they appear.

31:14.920 --> 31:17.760
Years ago, His Majesty
and the Duke of Ding shared a ruler.

31:18.280 --> 31:20.600
They split it in two, each keeping half.

31:21.120 --> 31:24.760
It symbolized their mutual trust and
commitment to counsel each other.

31:25.600 --> 31:28.760
But perhaps the relationship
between ruler and subject

31:29.280 --> 31:30.600
has always lacked true sentiment.

31:32.000 --> 31:32.960
My Lord,

31:33.880 --> 31:35.320
when His Grace returns to the capital,

31:35.840 --> 31:38.520
perhaps you can present
the ruler to His Majesty

31:39.120 --> 31:40.320
as a gesture of humility.

31:40.960 --> 31:43.640
Perhaps seeing the object

31:44.160 --> 31:46.680
will remind His Majesty of what once was.

31:48.440 --> 31:49.840
The way she looked at me

31:50.960 --> 31:52.000
was strange,

31:53.280 --> 31:54.920
as if we had met before.

31:55.880 --> 31:57.520
I can't quite figure her out yet.

31:58.920 --> 32:00.200
Having been away from the capital so long,

32:00.280 --> 32:01.440
I'm out of touch with court affairs.

32:01.520 --> 32:04.120
Investigate the Dou family thoroughly,
just to be safe.

32:04.920 --> 32:05.760
Yes, My Lord.

32:09.480 --> 32:10.320
Here.

32:21.840 --> 32:23.640
Young Lady, you stayed so calm
when staring down swords,

32:23.720 --> 32:25.120
but now that it's all over,

32:25.200 --> 32:26.440
why do you seem so shaken?

32:26.520 --> 32:29.040
That calmness was just an act.

32:29.840 --> 32:32.400
I've heard Song Mo has a way
of seeing right through people,

32:32.480 --> 32:35.040
like his gaze could
strip away every secret.

32:35.120 --> 32:37.560
Just thinking about it now
makes my heart pound with fear.

32:38.840 --> 32:41.040
I never want to see those eyes again.

32:41.920 --> 32:43.200
If he's so dangerous,

32:43.280 --> 32:44.520
why did you help him?

32:44.600 --> 32:47.280
You haven't seen him at his worst.

32:48.680 --> 32:50.680
If the Duke of Ding were
to truly die unjustly,

32:50.760 --> 32:52.400
with his nature,

32:52.480 --> 32:54.720
he'd likely do something far more insane.

32:55.240 --> 32:56.480
And that would be
a far greater catastrophe.

32:58.960 --> 32:59.960
By the way,

33:00.480 --> 33:01.960
did Grandmother
notice anything last night?

33:02.560 --> 33:05.840
She burned benzoin incense before bed.

33:05.920 --> 33:07.920
She slept deeply. I don't think
she has any idea what happened.

33:09.840 --> 33:11.760
-That's a relief.
-Zhao!

33:11.840 --> 33:13.320
An Su?

33:17.520 --> 33:18.800
-Zhao!
-An Su!

33:21.440 --> 33:22.760
Didn't you go to Futing with Zhang Ru?

33:22.840 --> 33:25.480
-Shou Gu! Su Su!
-Zhang Ru?

33:25.560 --> 33:26.920
Come to the front hall, there's good news!

33:27.000 --> 33:28.080
What good news?

33:28.160 --> 33:29.160
Just come!

33:30.120 --> 33:31.360
Old Madam Cui, congratulations!

33:31.440 --> 33:33.080
Young Master Ji has placed third
in the imperial exam,

33:33.160 --> 33:36.120
becoming the youngest
top scholar in our dynasty.

33:36.800 --> 33:40.240
Aside from that, after learning

33:40.320 --> 33:43.160
of your generous disaster relief efforts.

33:43.920 --> 33:48.400
Master Shi Ying has secured
a commendation for you from the court.

33:48.480 --> 33:51.560
We've all benefited greatly
from your support, Old Madam Cui.

33:52.440 --> 33:54.920
Tomorrow, we'll surely come
to share a celebratory drink

33:55.000 --> 33:56.560
and add to the joy.

33:57.080 --> 34:00.400
-All right, all right.
-We'll take our leave for now.

34:00.480 --> 34:01.640
Farewell, Old Madam.

34:01.720 --> 34:03.000
Please, no need to see us off.

34:04.200 --> 34:05.760
-Come out.
-You heard that, right?

34:05.840 --> 34:07.280
We're family here.

34:07.360 --> 34:09.040
Let's be open and honest.

34:10.639 --> 34:11.560
Come on.

34:14.960 --> 34:16.159
Grandmother.

34:18.679 --> 34:21.360
I suppose you've heard everything.

34:22.760 --> 34:24.080
Young Lady Zhao was worried

34:24.159 --> 34:26.040
about your relationship
with Master Shi Ying before.

34:26.719 --> 34:27.840
She can put her mind at ease now.

34:28.360 --> 34:29.520
With a little effort,

34:29.600 --> 34:32.320
there's no grudge between mother
and son that can't be resolved.

34:32.920 --> 34:34.920
Father has made such an effort.

34:35.000 --> 34:36.120
Grandmother, you must be pleased.

34:37.400 --> 34:39.920
Small gestures don't mean much to me.

34:42.000 --> 34:43.560
You won't admit it,

34:43.639 --> 34:46.400
but this morning you personally
made shepherd's purse wontons

34:46.480 --> 34:47.600
and sent them to Seventh Master.

34:48.840 --> 34:50.560
You talk too much,

34:50.639 --> 34:52.639
like a sieve leaking everything.

34:53.320 --> 34:55.320
Yes, yes. I'm sorry.

34:55.400 --> 34:58.880
Didn't you just say family should
always be open and honest?

34:58.960 --> 35:01.600
Yes, it's been a while
since we've seen you this happy.

35:01.680 --> 35:02.840
Just admit it.

35:04.000 --> 35:05.400
You little rascals.

35:05.480 --> 35:07.920
Fine, fine! I can't argue with you.

35:10.480 --> 35:12.040
The tutor has been praising Ming lately,

35:12.640 --> 35:14.280
saying her poetry is coming along well.

35:14.360 --> 35:16.880
Shi Ying, why don't you test her a little?

35:16.960 --> 35:19.360
Ming studies calligraphy,
poetry, and the arts

35:19.440 --> 35:22.080
for her own joy and relaxation.

35:22.160 --> 35:25.160
Testing her would just spoil her mood.

35:26.200 --> 35:27.240
Right.

35:28.080 --> 35:29.440
Master,

35:29.520 --> 35:30.920
why don't you take a break

35:31.000 --> 35:32.760
and have some dessert?

35:34.120 --> 35:37.040
Mother sent over some shepherd's purse
wontons this afternoon.

35:37.120 --> 35:38.920
I had several bowls.

35:39.000 --> 35:41.720
I'm really full.

35:44.440 --> 35:45.360
Father,

35:45.880 --> 35:48.680
Mother knows
you've been busy and stressed.

35:48.760 --> 35:51.800
She spent the whole afternoon
preparing sweet taro with osmanthus.

35:51.880 --> 35:53.680
It's perfect for soothing
and replenishing your energy.

35:57.360 --> 35:58.560
Bring me a bowl.

36:08.960 --> 36:12.440
Something sweet after a full meal
sounds just right.

36:13.600 --> 36:16.080
So you like shepherd's purse wontons.

36:16.160 --> 36:18.240
I'll make them for you more often.

36:20.240 --> 36:22.720
I often had stomach trouble
when I was little.

36:23.240 --> 36:25.760
Mother would pick shepherd's purse
and make wontons for me.

36:25.840 --> 36:27.160
It always made me feel better.

36:28.880 --> 36:31.240
After she moved to the estate,

36:31.760 --> 36:33.000
others tried making it,

36:33.520 --> 36:34.480
but it was never quite the same.

36:38.000 --> 36:39.200
In a few days,

36:39.280 --> 36:41.000
the commendation I requested
for Mother will arrive.

36:42.120 --> 36:43.880
It'll be the perfect opportunity

36:43.960 --> 36:45.880
to invite her to return
to the capital with me

36:45.960 --> 36:47.320
so I can care for her properly.

36:47.400 --> 36:48.720
What do you think, Ying Xue?

36:50.400 --> 36:53.520
You've worked hard
to secure this honor for Mother.

36:54.040 --> 36:55.560
If this brings reconciliation,

36:55.640 --> 36:57.440
it'll be a blessing for the our family.

36:58.080 --> 37:00.040
Hearing you say that puts my mind at ease.

37:01.800 --> 37:03.800
Master, Commissioner Lu has arrived.

37:04.720 --> 37:06.400
Invite him to Tongwen Hall
and serve him tea.

37:06.920 --> 37:07.960
Yes, Master.

37:14.400 --> 37:15.400
Please excuse me.

37:25.200 --> 37:26.080
Master?

37:26.720 --> 37:27.560
I'm fine.

37:28.240 --> 37:29.120
Mother,

37:29.640 --> 37:31.400
Father still cares about you.

37:31.480 --> 37:34.160
He was already full,
but he still ate your dessert.

37:35.720 --> 37:37.320
Cares about me?

37:37.840 --> 37:39.800
But he clearly cares about them more.

37:40.800 --> 37:43.600
When that old hag brings Dou Zhao back,

37:43.680 --> 37:46.160
will there even be a place for us
to have a say in this family?

37:46.680 --> 37:48.200
CUI'S RESIDENCE

37:49.720 --> 37:52.640
Uncle Shi Shu spent ten years
just to pass the imperial exam.

37:52.720 --> 37:54.000
Young Master Ji is much smarter.

37:54.080 --> 37:55.480
So young,

37:55.560 --> 37:57.320
and he ranked third on his first try.

37:57.400 --> 38:00.000
If it were me,
I'd throw banquets everywhere,

38:00.080 --> 38:01.640
brag to all my relatives,
and soak in the glory.

38:01.720 --> 38:03.280
But what does he do?

38:03.360 --> 38:04.600
He doesn't even come back.

38:05.520 --> 38:08.280
He's never liked
celebrating with banquets.

38:08.360 --> 38:10.560
He'd just find it boring
and a waste of time.

38:10.640 --> 38:13.320
Only you could understand
his odd personality.

38:13.840 --> 38:15.680
Still, passing the exam
is a good thing, isn't it?

38:15.760 --> 38:17.960
But look at his letter,
it's full of frustration.

38:18.040 --> 38:20.240
When His Majesty asked him
about his ambitions,

38:20.320 --> 38:22.440
he said he wanted to become
Grand Secretary within ten years

38:22.520 --> 38:24.160
and reform the government.

38:24.240 --> 38:25.440
That's an impressive ambition!

38:25.520 --> 38:27.320
But this isn't some opera performance.

38:27.400 --> 38:28.600
He was too bold.

38:28.680 --> 38:31.080
His Majesty rebuked him, saying
he chased fame and fortune.

38:31.160 --> 38:32.680
His talk of reform

38:32.760 --> 38:34.720
practically branded
the entire court as corrupt.

38:34.800 --> 38:36.120
How could they tolerate that?

38:37.320 --> 38:39.520
His Majesty denied him
the top scholar title

38:39.600 --> 38:40.960
and a position in the Hanlin Academy.

38:41.480 --> 38:43.240
Instead, he sent him to Futing
to observe and assist.

38:43.840 --> 38:45.080
With Ji Yong's pride,

38:45.600 --> 38:46.880
how could he accept that?

38:46.960 --> 38:50.520
Forget it. Someone like him would
never make a good match for our family.

38:50.600 --> 38:52.120
He's impossible to figure out.

38:52.920 --> 38:54.720
Aren't you going to have some?

38:54.800 --> 38:57.000
Later. I have to write him a reply first.

39:12.080 --> 39:17.080
REVERING HEAVEN AND HONORING ANCESTORS

39:19.400 --> 39:20.320
Your Majesty,

39:20.960 --> 39:23.360
it is precisely because the Duke of Ding
has abused his power,

39:23.440 --> 39:24.440
and indulged in debauchery

39:24.520 --> 39:26.560
that Futing has been overrun
by corrupt officials,

39:26.640 --> 39:29.040
plagued by recurring floods,
and caused the people to suffer.

39:29.120 --> 39:31.040
Tomorrow, please submit memorials

39:31.640 --> 39:34.920
to impeach the Duke of Ding for
abusing his power, acting tyrannically.

39:37.760 --> 39:40.000
-Yes, My Lord.
-Minister, surely you haven't forgotten

39:41.000 --> 39:43.240
that it was the Duke of Ding

39:43.760 --> 39:47.080
who ensured ten years of uninterrupted
maritime trade in Futing?

39:47.160 --> 39:48.280
Are you saying

39:48.800 --> 39:50.800
all that credit belongs to him alone?

39:52.480 --> 39:54.520
Your father is the Minister of Personnel.

39:54.600 --> 39:57.000
Have him accuse the Duke of Ding
of laziness and autocratic behavior.

39:57.080 --> 39:57.960
Got it.

39:58.040 --> 40:00.240
Your father is
the Vice Minister of Revenue.

40:00.840 --> 40:03.080
Have him criticize His Grace
for neglecting his wife.

40:03.160 --> 40:04.560
Being autocratic, got it.

40:04.640 --> 40:06.160
Neglecting his wife, got it.

40:06.680 --> 40:07.880
That's not yours.

40:07.960 --> 40:08.840
Your father's should be…

40:10.720 --> 40:11.600
Never mind, it's the same.

40:11.680 --> 40:13.760
The Duke of Ding's laziness and autocracy

40:13.840 --> 40:15.000
must be punished.

40:15.080 --> 40:17.520
He should be reassigned
to a harsh borderland post

40:17.600 --> 40:19.240
to prevent any further trouble.

40:19.320 --> 40:21.560
As the commander of an army,

40:21.640 --> 40:24.080
he has openly neglected
his wife and exploited others.

40:24.160 --> 40:25.280
His lack of heirs

40:25.360 --> 40:27.280
is proof of his unfilial behavior.

40:27.880 --> 40:29.520
Minister, I must disagree.

40:29.600 --> 40:32.480
The Duke of Ding's Army's embezzlement
of military funds is a grave crime.

40:33.000 --> 40:35.120
I implore Your Majesty
to impose severe punishment

40:35.200 --> 40:36.840
to preserve the foundation of the state.

40:37.520 --> 40:39.320
I delivered your message
exactly as you said,

40:39.840 --> 40:41.320
but I still don't understand.

40:41.400 --> 40:42.560
Why have the officials

40:43.080 --> 40:45.200
submit impeachment requests
that contradict each other?

40:45.800 --> 40:46.640
That's the point.

40:47.160 --> 40:49.640
When His Majesty hears their baseless
accusations and incoherent arguments,

40:49.720 --> 40:52.480
he'll realize my uncle is a loyal subject,
with no factions or allies.

40:52.560 --> 40:55.200
His suspicions and distrust
will naturally dissipate.

40:59.760 --> 41:01.280
Contradictions upon contradictions…

41:03.040 --> 41:04.560
This is all nonsense.

41:12.640 --> 41:13.760
Your Majesty…

41:21.480 --> 41:23.320
-Can you believe…?
-I know.

41:29.520 --> 41:31.080
Grand Secretary, Grand Secretary!

41:35.120 --> 41:37.240
What I said before His Majesty
wasn't directed at you.

41:37.840 --> 41:41.040
I had to answer
His Majesty's question impartially.

41:43.320 --> 41:44.960
Impartially…

41:45.480 --> 41:48.240
For the sake of stabilizing
the court, you did right.

41:49.040 --> 41:51.680
But this matter concerns
major issues in the southeast.

41:52.320 --> 41:54.600
It has nothing to do with
the Ministry of Rites, right?

41:57.680 --> 41:58.920
It's the time of the Dragon Boat Festival.

41:59.720 --> 42:05.040
Minister Dou, why don't you
take a few days off to rest at home?

42:08.480 --> 42:09.640
Since you've said so,

42:09.720 --> 42:11.120
I'll follow your instruction.

42:42.720 --> 42:44.400
Young Master Wu Shan is unconscious.

42:44.480 --> 42:46.000
Young Lady Zhao has ordered him carried
to the open area in the back courtyard.

42:46.080 --> 42:48.600
How dare you harm
Grand Secretary Wu's only grandson!

42:48.680 --> 42:50.840
By the time the doctor arrives,
Young Master Wu will already be dead.

42:50.920 --> 42:53.080
Dou Zhao, are you trying to
get the whole family killed?

42:54.000 --> 42:56.600
Since you can read people,
you can tell I'm not lying.

42:57.120 --> 42:58.080
I can save him.

44:47.840 --> 44:48.880
NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
DURING THE MAKING OF THIS FILM

44:48.960 --> 44:50.680
MEDICAL ACTS AND DRUGS IN THIS DRAMA
ARE FICTIONAL. DO NOT IMITATE.
